<TEXT>
textilestate lawmakers racing to gain 
approval of their embattled importlimiting bill before congress 
adjourns confess anxiety over fresh delays being threatened in the 
house 
they could outdistance us we just dont have that much time 
in this congress sen ernest f hollings dsc said thursday 
