and is engaged to a fifth 
christians find that a monogamous marital union provides the 
foundation upon which to build a stable family in accordance with 
the original plan of god for marriage the pope told a crowd of 
about 10000 people 
hence any forms of disregard for the equal dignity of men and 
women must be seen as serious contradiction of the truth that 
chirst the king of peace brought into the world 
