<TEXT>
almost all the men who ignored the warnings 
and gave the goahead for the challenger launch are gone and new 
ones are in place as the shuttle program returns to flight 
one shuttle astronaut richard truly now is at the helm of 
nasas spaceflight program another robert crippen who has been 
on four shuttle missions will give the final nod to commit 
discovery and other future shuttles to flight 
the top officials of morton thiokol which built the booster 
rocket that doomed the challenger are gone gone too is most of 
