in the automotive products division rk lund vice president of 
advanced technology and calvin wiggins general manager of the 
huntsville division jerald e mason boss of the booster division 
retired early 
roger boisjoly a thiokol engineer said the company harassed 
him for his strong testimony before the rogers commission and sued 
thiokol for billions of dollars the case was dismissed and he has 
left the company long ago 
