<TEXT>
ames department stores will jump from 
fifth place to third among the nations largest discount retailers 
with its acquisition of zayre corps 388 discount stores ames 
president said 
we will also gain entry into new and profitable markets such 
as florida and illinois as well as increase our penetration in 
other markets peter hollis ames president and chief executive 
officer said thursday 
the deal announced thursday was valued at about 800 million 
company officials said 
ames currently operates 348 discount stores primarily in small 
towns in 18 states in the northeast and midatlantic region 
with the deal ames will have its first stores in florida and 
illinois as well as alabama georgia lousiana mississippi 
tennessee and wisconsin said catherine g leonard ames director 
of investor relations 
zayre discount stores are similar to ames stores although some 
are located in larger metropolitan areas in 26 states leonard 
said the two chains have 12 stores that compete in the same 
communities leonard said 
ames marketing strategy has been to locate in small towns and 
operate as oldfashioned general stores about 45 percent of its 
inventory is apparel and domestic items such as sheets pillow 
cases and rugs 
the remaining 55 percent is hard line hardware houseware 
jewelry health and beauty aids and automobile parts 
leonard said no decision had been made on the possible closing 
of some stores or possible layoffs 
one of the first things we will do is study all zayre 
locations for their longterm profit potential she said 
ames chairman james a harmon said the company had been 
analyzing the zayre discount business for several months 
the transaction has been extensively studied from every point 
of view we believe it is a unique opportunity under most favorable 
terms he said 
in the fiscal year ended jan 30 ames had revenue of 21 
billion and net income of 342 million in addition to its 
discount stores ames operates 161 smaller variety stores under the 
gc murphy variety stores name 
framingham massbased zayre stores currently the nations 
fourth largest discount retailer had annual sales of 35 billion 
last year and a profit of 1433 million 
its discount stores however werent profitable posting 
losses last year 
zayres other businesses include tj maxx hit or miss and miss 
chadwicks of boston inc 
ames said zayre will receive cash 200 million in subordinated 
notes and preferred stock convertible to 8 million shares of ames 
common stock at a price of 25 a share 
zayre will own a 175 percent share of ames stock when the deal 
is completed leonard said but a 10year agreement was put into 
effect that limits zayre to owning a maximum of 20 percent of the 
voting securities of ames 
zayre said in a statement that its estimated net cash proceeds 
would be 620 million after expenses and refinancing of the 
subordinate note 
the company said that after paying about 250 million in 
shortterm debt it plans to use a substantial portion of the 
balance to benefit shareholders possibly through a major stock 
buyback 
zayre also said it will incur a onetime charge in the third 
quarter of about 110 million because of the discontinued 
operations 
we are pleased to be able to enhance the value of our shares 
through the redeployment of our assets as evidenced by this 
transaction zayre chairman maurice segall said 
ames said zayre will have the right to nominate two directors 
the boards of both companies have approved the deal which is 
still subject to regulatory approval and completion of ames 
financing ames said it has a commitment from citibank na 
the transaction was expected to be completed in 45 days 
