costs it has fewer than 600 employees in the united states down 
from an average of 2500 a year ago 
the company produces cabbage patch kids alf dolls big wheels 
palstic tricycles and board games such as scrabble industry 
sources say the company controls about 5 percent of the nations 
toy market 
